text: Add brain tips for _io.TextIOWrapper's buffer and raw attributes.
Use astroid_cache instead of MANAGER.builtins(), since that does not exist in this release.
Rename a couple of finders and document them.
Fix some pylint errors over the code base.
Export __version__ in __init__.
Add support for discovering .pth file created by certain namespace packages.
Forgot to make _import a package.
Move the spec finder under a new namespace, interpreter._import.

Add pytest 3 compatibility in brain_pytest (#357)

This change adjusts brain_pytest for pytest 3, while also reintroducing pytest 2 compatibility.
